data.description:
Discover the ideal living space in this spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom split-level home nestled in a quaint neighborhood. Situated on an ample 8,266 sq ft lot, this property offers a world of possibilities.
The main level opens to a large back deck, providing an inviting outdoor space perfect for relaxation and entertainment. Downstairs, you'll find a versatile area that could serve as an extra living space, or the canvas for a potential apartment conversion, offering endless creative opportunities.
For those with storage needs, this home boasts plenty of space throughout, ensuring you can keep your living areas organized and clutter-free. The downstairs even features its own private small deck, adding to the charm of the property. Don't miss this rare find in Eureka Springs. Schedule a showing today and imagine the potential that awaits you in this versatile split-level gem.
